"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-luxolo-adams-not-in-shape-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 17 July 2024 05:10 pm Luxolo Adams in action during last year's World Athletics Championships in Budapest.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 93, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\", \"score\": 0.9999999998044586, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luxolo Adams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\"}, {\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999683672707429, \"rank\": 2.694315942638657e-05, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 168, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9989231555573878, \"rank\": 0.001078005021730945, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"17 July 2024 05:10 pm\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 86}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Anton Geyser/Gallo Images Now that he's run twice over the last couple of weeks, it is clear that Luxolo Adams should not go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 193, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.3385251517535218e-13, \"text\": \"Geyser\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\"}, {\"begin\": 200, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"score\": 0.861793459552865, \"rank\": 0.09938633117515507, \"text\": \"Gallo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\", \"score\": 0.9999999998044586, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luxolo Adams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxolo_Adams\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The removal of the 27-year-old sprinter from the SA team for the Paris Games has not only caused controversy but haslanded up in court.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999979220850707, \"rank\": 2.0776194958905746e-06, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The removal\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"the 27-year-old sprinter\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adams, however, should not be selected ahead ofWayde van Niekerkfor the 200m event in the French capital.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.983230941407874, \"rank\": 0.011821588974013945, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m event\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not to say Adams does not have a legal case.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"a legal case\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was initially included in the team, and then removed, and Athletics South Africa's qualifying criteria does not seem to give the federation much leeway to select athletes based on form.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athletics South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"the federation\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"much leeway\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But picking Adams would be a mistake because he's not in shape.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he has apparently recovered from a hamstring injury that derailed the first half of his 2024 campaign, in his only two 200m races this year, Adams clocked 21.50 in Italy earlier this month and 21.31 in Switzerland on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8312287898710873, \"rank\": 0.17510265969858518, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9928604534994763, \"rank\": 0.006957578197742283, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hamstring injury\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"his 2024 campaign\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"his only two 200m races\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To put this into perspective, his season's bestranks him 67th in South Africain the 200m sprint, and the country has 19 junior athletes (including two 15-year-old sprinters) who have run quicker than him this year.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"South Africain\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m sprint\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"19 junior athletes\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"two 15-year-old sprinters\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reality is that five South African athletes have achieved the qualifying criteria in the 200m event, and only three can go to Paris.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999154404158, \"rank\": 8.45595185444202e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reality\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"five South African athletes\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying criteria\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m event\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a scenario like this, where two athletes are going to miss out, it makes sense for ASA to pick the three athletes who are in the best shape, which is what they have done by selecting Shaun Maswanganyi,Benjamin Richardsonand Van Niekerk (ahead of Adams and Sinesipho Dambile).\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"score\": 0.9093515812893389, \"rank\": 0.08316463708193023, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_Maswanganyi\", \"score\": 0.9999968692872139, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun Maswanganyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_Maswanganyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_Maswanganyi\"}, {\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.8994271796314548, \"rank\": 0.10956745416722083, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a scenario\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"two athletes\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the three athletes\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shape\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"Sinesipho Dambile\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Adams wins his court case, and ASA is forced to select him, it means Van Niekerk will be dropped from the squad and will not be able to compete in the 4x100m or 4x400m relays, which puts a dent in the nation's medal hopes.\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"score\": 0.9093515812893389, \"rank\": 0.08316463708193023, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adams\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"his court case\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"m or 4x400m relays\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"a dent\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's medal\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It must bedisappointing for Adamsto have lost his spot, but he needs to admit that he's not fit enough to represent his country right now and should focus on regaining his form, rather than forcing ASA to spend money on legal costs to fight the matter in court.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"score\": 0.9093515812893389, \"rank\": 0.08316463708193023, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Film_speed\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adamsto\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"his form\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"legal costs\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The federation has made the right decision.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The federation\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the right decision\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2325, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9926441253696738, \"rank\": 0.007410077516345784, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: